  openbsd_pf_pf_blacklist_template
    Description: Define the template source for 'pf.blacklist.j2'.
                 Any value other than 'default' requires a Jinja2 file to be
                 created. The custom Jinja2 file for an example configuration
                 called 'example' needs to be placed as follows:
                 'openbsd_pf/templates/example/pf.blacklist.j2'
    Implemented: 0.1
    Required   : False
    Value      : Arbitrary
    Type       : String
    Default    : 'default'
    Options    :
      Examples: 'example' | 'environment' | 'hostname'

